etphoneshome.entities.enemies

Class Enemy

  • java.lang.Object
    • etphoneshome.entities.enemies.Enemy
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Police, Scientist

    public class Enemy
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used as the parent class for the various enemy characters. Using the getLocation method returns a location object. Using setLocation allows you to set the enemy's location to a specified location. Using getIsDead checks if this enemy is currently dead. Using setIsDead allows you to set whether this enemy is currently dead.
